When I'm in downtown Phoenix, I frequently visit this spot and sit at the martini bar. Everything from their classic cocktails to their outstanding food, the bartenders also cut and prepare fresh meat and cheese platters right in front of you. On weekends, DJ up-top will spin classic hiphop music..just enough to set the vibe for good conversation and bumping your head but not loud enough where it's a club.

